It was a pleasure to join @RepKevinHern and @GOPpolicy this afternoon for a “Meet The Experts” panel on the important issue of protecting women’s sports. 

Grown men competing against - and being allowed to change in women’s locker rooms - is wrong! 

@POTUS, and our Republican Majority in Congress, are putting an end to this madness. 🏃‍♀️

Just moments ago, I introduced my first bill in Congress - the FIGHTER Act (Fortifying Income by Giving our Heroes their Earned Tax Relief). 🇺🇸 

@POTUS has affirmed a mandate to strengthen our military, care for our warfighters, and secure that it is the best it can be. This bill is about honoring those commitments and will provide immediate and meaningful, long-term reduction in tax burdens for those who serve to defend our freedoms.

The FIGHTER Act strengthens military families, supports recruitment and retention efforts, and helps ensure America stands ready to meet our challenges ahead.
